 the golden boot as the tournaments top scorer with five goals and three assists at the  world cup he played a major role in helping the team win the trophy scoring five goals and receiving the silver ball as the tounaments second top player and the silver boot as the second top goalscorer and was also named in the world cup all star xi and in the dream team in  müller was ranked the fifthbest footballer in the world by the guardian contents  club career  early career  bayern munich  – season  – season  – season  – season  – season  – season  – season  – season  international career   world cup  euro    world cup  euro   style of play  personal life  career statistics  club  international  international goals  honours  club  country  individual  references  external links club careeredit early careeredit born in weilheim müller played as a youth for tsv pähl and at the age of  he made the  km journey to join local bundesliga side bayern munich in  he progressed through the youth system and was part of the team that finished runnerup in the under  bundesliga in  he made his debut for the reserve team in march  when he replaced stephan fürstner in a regionalliga match against spvgg unterhaching in which he scored he made two more regionalliga appearances in the – season while continuing to play for the under team the following season bayerns second string qualified for the newly formed  liga and müller established himself as a key player – he played in  out of  matches and scored  times to make him the leagues fifth top scorer he also became involved in the firstteam under then manager jürgen klinsmann he appeared in preseason friendlies and made his full debut on  august  when he came on as a substitute for miroslav klose for the last ten minutes of a bundesliga match against hamburger sv despite müller feeling that his performance did not go well he made three more bundesliga appearances that season and made his champions league debut on  march  when he was substituted on in the nd minute for bastian schweinsteiger in a – win over sporting cp he scored bayerns last goal as they won the tie – on aggregate bayern munichedit in february  müller signed his first contract for the senior team a twoyear deal effective from the – season along with reserve teammate holger badstuber – seasonedit see also – fc bayern munich season müller was prepared to be loaned or even transferred away to find firstteam football but when louis van gaal was appointed manager both players became fixtures in the bayern first team from the start of the season in the first few matches müller was a regular substitute and on  september  he was brought on against borussia dortmund and scored two goals in a – victory three days later he scored another brace in a – champions league victory over maccabi haifa he rounded off september by being named the bundesliga player of the month and earned praise from his namesake legendary former bayern and germany striker gerd müller after the haifa match müller was in the starting xi for almost every match only missing one match a champions league match against bordeaux for which he was suspended because he was sent off in an earlier match against the same team in february  müller signed a new contract with bayern munich through  during the second half of the season müller continued to be a regular firstteam starter usually playing in a central striking role due to the availability of other wide players franck ribéry and arjen robben in april  he scored the second goal in a – win against title rivals schalke  and in the penultimate league match of the season he scored the first hattrick of his career in a – win over vfl bochum which effectively secured the german title for bayern the title was confirmed a week later with a – win at hertha bsc a match which müller started for the season he played in all  bundesliga matches starting  and recorded  goals and  assists bayern and müller were back in berlin the following week to face werder bremen in the final of the dfbpokal müller started the match and bayern won – to complete the domestic double müller scored four goals and made two assists during the competition which made him its leading scorer for the season bayerns season ended in pursuit of a first treble in the  champions league final against inter milano at santiago bernabéu stadium in madrid it was not to be however as they lost – with both goals coming from diego milito müller was in the starting lineup and had a key chance just after halftime with bayern – down but his shot was saved by júlio césar müller felt particularly disappointed by this defeat but he ended his first season as a firstteam player with  matches played and  goals in all competitions in a poll conducted by the sports magazine kicker he was voted by his fellow professionals as the best newcomer of the – season and was named in the bundesliga team of the season müller credits van gaal for having had the biggest part to play in his rise to success – the coach arrived with a reputation for promoting youth team players particularly at ajax and consistently gave müller his chance in the firstteam going as far to say müller spielt bei mir immer with me müller will always play müller in return described van gaal as a genius technician who makes players improve every time – seasonedit see also – fc bayern munich season müller with bayern munich in saint petersburg russia may  müller returned from his postworld cup break to sign another contract extension this time extending his stay at bayern until  as with all of bayerns world cup participants he missed much of preseason and his first match back was the supercup against schalke  on  august he was named in the starting  and scored the opening goal in a – win two weeks later he scored the opening goal of bayerns league season in a – home win against vfl wolfsburg müller played in every match of the first half of the season usually as a starter but as the team struggled for results müller was unable to match the previous seasons goalscoring exploits being dropped to the bench and even receiving a telling off from louis van gaal after missing an easy chance in a – defeat against  fc kaiserslautern in august he was philosophical about this dip in form though and after eight league games without a goal he scored in a – win against eintracht frankfurt on  november he followed that by scoring in consecutive league and cup wins against vfb stuttgart three weeks later these goals took his tally to eight goals in all competitions and included a spectacular goal to open the scoring in a – champions league victory against roma on  september as his team was on its winter break müller was left to reflect on what he described as an almost unbelievable first year as a pro müller began the second half of the season in good form but was involved in an altercation with teammate arjen robben who was angered when müller showed his displeasure at a poor freekick robben took during a – win at werder bremen müller again played in every game of the season and scored  goals  in the league but the season was less successful for bayern as they finished third in the league and were knocked out of the dfbpokal in the semifinals by schalke  and in the round of  of the uefa champions league by inter milan bayern had won – at the san siro and müller scored  minutes into the second leg to make it – on aggregate but inter levelled the score at – in the th minute to go through on the away goals rule müllers mentor van gaal was increasingly criticised for inflexibility in tactical transfer and selection policy and ultimately lost his job being replaced with jupp heynckes – seasonedit see also – fc bayern munich season in bayerns first dfbpokal game müller was awarded the man of the match after earning two penalties which were converted by mario gómez and bastian schweinsteiger müller then added a third in the closing stages to secure a – victory over eintracht braunschweig it took müller five matches for him to get his first league goal he scored it against schalke  in bayerns – win müller then scored in bayerns next home game in the early stages of the match which the went on to win – on  november  müller netted the opener on the halfhour in bayerns – thrashing of fc ingolstadt giving him his second dfbpokal goal müller was on the shortlist of this years fifa ballon dor award on  and  january in bayerns warm up friendlies müller scored three goals in two games a brace against the india national team which bayern then went on to win – and one goal in bayerns other – victory over rotweiß erfurt müller provided two assists in bayerns win over vfb stuttgart in the dfbpokal on  february bayern played  fc kaiserslautern and müller ended a goal drought lasting since  september  with a header in their – victory on  march  müller played his th bundesliga game against  fc nürnberg on  may  müller scored the opening goal in the champions league final against chelsea with a powerful header he was substituted shortly afterwards bayern munich however lost the final on penalties müller stated how dissatisfied he was about the amount of time he had spent on the bench recently müller said that although he was dissatisfied he wanted to stay at bayern during the season müller scored seven goals in  league matches two goals in five german cup matches and two goals in  champions league matches – seasonedit see also – fc bayern munich season müllers first bundesliga goal of the season came over  bundesliga champions spvgg greuther fürth in bayerns – victory on  august  on  september he netted a brace as bayern thrashed southern rivals vfb stuttgart – in front of  at the newly expanded allianz arena müller helped bayern achieve a recordbreaking start to the league season when he netted a brace over newly promoted fortuna düsseldorf on  october in their – victory recording bayerns eighth successive win three days later he scored his first champions league goal of the season netting from the penalty spot as bayern defeated lille – at the french sides newly built grand stade lille métropole on  december after his good run of form in the first half of the bundesliga season müller pledged his allegiance claiming he was at home in munich and that there is no club to step up from when you leave fc bayern there almost is no better club six days later he signed a twoyear contract extension keeping him at the allianz arena until  at the winter break in the bundesliga he had nine goals and seven assists in  league appearances and a further three goals in the champions league this gave him a total of  goals halfway through the season including his strike against borussia dortmund in bayerns win in the  dflsupercup müller scored his first goal in bayerns second game back from the break in a – away win over vfb stuttgart müller tapped in his fifth goal of the champions league campaign on  april completing a – first leg defeat of juventus in the quarterfinals ending the italian clubs match unbeaten record in europe on  april  müller scored two goals and gave one assist in – win against barcelona in the champions league semifinal in the allianz arena on the return fixture müller scored a header as bayern won – and gave barcelona their biggest defeat ever in the champions league with a – aggregate score müller then went on to play an important role in bayerns – victory over borussia dortmund in the final on  june müller scored a penalty in the final of the – dfbpokal bayern won the cup – to complete an historic treble müller scored  goals overall in the season including all competitions netting  in the bundesliga one in the pokal and an impressive eight in the champions league he also added one in the  dflsupercup which bayern won – this topped off müllers highest scoring season to date – seasonedit see also – fc bayern munich season müller with bayern in  müller began the – season by playing in the german super cup by scoring in seven of bayerns  preseason games his first competitive match came against borussia dortmund in the german super cup on  august müller scored a hattrick as bayern won – in the teams – dfbpokal firstround game against schwarzweiß rehden in bayerns opening – bundesliga fixture müller missed a penalty for the first time seconds later the save from the penalty flicked the hand of álvaro domínguez which resulted in another penalty which david alaba converted after this müller stated i am still happy to take penalties but i think david alaba is the main man for spot kicks for now he played in the uefa super cup on  september against hannover  in the second round of the dfbpokal müller scored twice taking his cup tally to five goals in just two games on  september müller scored the only goal in a – victory over vfl wolfsburg giving him his first goal in the – bundesliga müller scored his first – uefa champions league goal of the campaign and bayern defeated manchester city – at the city of manchester stadium on  october he played in a match at the fifa club world cup on  may  müller scored bayerns second goal in a – extratime defeat of borussia dortmund in the  dfbpokal final giving die roten the tenth league and cup double in their history müller finished as the tournaments top scorer with eight goals in five appearances he finished the season by scoring  goals in  league matches eight goals in five dfbpokal matches and five goals in  champions league matches – seasonedit see also – fc bayern munich season after the – season müller signed a new contract keeping him at bayern until  and rejected a contract offer from manchester united müller played in the dflsupercup which was bayerns first match in the – season bayern lost the match – his first goal of the season was against preußen münster in the dfbpokal on  august  then in the opening match of the bundesliga on  august  müller scored the opening goal of bayerns bundesliga season against vfl wolfsburg bayern went