n in the  dflsupercup müller scored his first goal in bayerns second game back from the break in a – away win over vfb stuttgart müller tapped in his fifth goal of the champions league campaign on  april completing a – first leg defeat of juventus in the quarterfinals ending the italian clubs match unbeaten record in europe on  april  müller scored two goals and gave one assist in – win against barcelona in the champions league semifinal in the allianz arena on the return fixture müller scored a header as bayern won – and gave barcelona their biggest defeat ever in the champions league with a – aggregate score müller then went on to play an important role in bayerns – victory over borussia dortmund in the final on  june müller scored a penalty in the final of the – dfbpokal bayern won the cup – to complete an historic treble müller scored  goals overall in the season including all competitions netting  in the bundesliga one in the pokal and an impressive eight in the champions league he also added one in the  dflsupercup which bayern won – this topped off müllers highest scoring season to date – seasonedit see also – fc bayern munich season müller with bayern in  müller began the – season by playing in the german super cup by scoring in seven of bayerns  preseason games his first competitive match came against borussia dortmund in the german super cup on  august müller scored a hattrick as bayern won – in the teams – dfbpokal firstround game against schwarzweiß rehden in bayerns opening – bundesliga fixture müller missed a penalty for the first time seconds later the save from the penalty flicked the hand of álvaro domínguez which resulted in another penalty which david alaba converted after this müller stated i am still happy to take penalties but i think david alaba is the main man for spot kicks for now he played in the uefa super cup on  september against hannover  in the second round of the dfbpokal müller scored twice taking his cup tally to five goals in just